《'''山村犹有读书声'''》（Être et avoir）是一部2002年法国纪录电影，[[尼古拉·菲利贝尔|尼古拉·菲利贝尔]]执导。它被提名2002年[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]非竞赛单元<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/3158545/year/2002.html |title=Festival de Cannes: To Be and to Have |accessdate=2009-11-03 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2012-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010001522/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/3158545/year/2002.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并获得了商业成功。<ref name="guardian 04-10-03">{{cite news
|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2004/oct/03/film.france
|publisher=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]
|author=Amelia Gentleman
|title=Film's fallen hero fights on for his class
